        <h2>Cheerleading-Specific Planning</h2>
        <p>Cheer teams are typically 10-25 athletes. Their banquet can be combined with the athletic department celebration or held separately as a squad-only event.</p>

        <h3>Cheerleading Decor Themes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Spirit Central</strong> — Pom poms, megaphones, and team-colored decorations throughout</li>
          <li><strong>All-Star Cheer</strong> — Glamorous theme with sparkling accents and cheer action photos</li>
          <li><strong>Competition Champions</strong> — Highlight competition season with trophy/medal displays</li>
        </ul>

