        </div>

        <h2>Cheerleading Award Categories</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>All-Around Cheerleader</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Most Spirited</strong> — The athlete who brings energy to every event</li>
          <li><strong>Best Technique</strong> — Most skilled in motions, jumps, tumbling</li>
          <li><strong>Best Flyer / Best Base / Best Backspot</strong> — Stunt group recognition</li>
          <li><strong>Most Improved</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Leadership Award</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Perfect Attendance</strong></li>
        </ul>

